WEBVTT

00:03.106 --> 00:05.608
Uh-huh, and when did you
stop eating meat?

00:05.610 --> 00:07.343
Uh, like, uh, yesterday.

00:07.345 --> 00:08.978
- Oh, really?
- Yup.

00:08.980 --> 00:10.679
Morning, Rakesh.

00:10.681 --> 00:12.815
Good morning!
Hey, Ashley.

00:12.817 --> 00:13.849
Is the mango juice back in?

00:13.851 --> 00:15.050
Where it usually is.

00:15.052 --> 00:16.852
Yes!

00:16.854 --> 00:17.853
What's with the mango juice?

00:17.855 --> 00:18.954
I just like it.

00:18.956 --> 00:20.356
Whatever happened
to apple juice?

00:20.358 --> 00:22.558
- That's for little kids.
- Oh, of course.

00:22.560 --> 00:25.261
Mango juice has lots of
vitamins. You should try it.

00:25.263 --> 00:28.097
Uh, coffee's got all the
vitamins I need in the morning.

00:28.099 --> 00:29.865
Hey!

00:29.867 --> 00:30.933
Come on, you know what this is.

00:30.935 --> 00:32.801
Give me the money.
- Okay.

00:32.803 --> 00:34.570
Give me the money!
Come on, now! Shut up!

00:34.572 --> 00:35.546
- Please, please?
-Shut up!

00:35.570 --> 00:36.740
Please, okay.

00:36.741 --> 00:38.007
Come on, let's go, man!

00:38.009 --> 00:39.441
Right now!
- I'm ope-opening.

00:39.443 --> 00:40.709
Don't be stupid! Let's go!

00:40.711 --> 00:42.244
Now! Shut up!
Calm down, okay.

00:42.246 --> 00:44.213
Come on! Hurry up!
Let's go!

00:44.215 --> 00:45.681
Do it! Hurry up!
- Okay.

00:45.683 --> 00:47.316
Open it now!

00:48.518 --> 00:49.852
No! Daddy!

00:49.854 --> 00:53.088
Man, what'd you do?!

00:53.090 --> 00:54.323
Don't move!

00:55.192 --> 00:56.425
What you standing around for?

00:56.427 --> 00:57.960
We got to go!

00:59.000 --> 01:05.074
